<!-- EDIT TEMPLATE DOCUMENTATION BELOW THIS LINE -->

This template returns the English abbreviation (between "Jan" and "Dec") of the month whose number is in parameter. Alternatively, the English name or abbreviation (in any letter case) can be provided.
; Syntax<nowiki>:</nowiki>
: <tt><nowiki>{{</nowiki>MONTHABBREV|</tt>''month''<tt>}}</tt>
* The ''month'' value is interpreted modulo 12 (extra leading zeroes and decimals are ignored).

; Examples for all standard English month names<nowiki>:</nowiki>
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|january}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|january}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|february}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|february}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|march}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|march}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|april}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|april}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|may}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|may}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|june}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|june}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|july}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|july}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|august}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|august}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|september}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|september}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|october}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|october}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|november}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|november}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|december}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|december}}

; Examples for all abbreviated English month names<nowiki>:</nowiki>
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|JAN}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|JAN}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|FEB}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|FEB}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|MAR}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|MAR}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|APR}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|APR}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|MAY}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|MAY}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|JUN}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|JUN}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|JUL}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|JUL}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|AUG}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|AUG}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|SEP}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|SEP}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|OCT}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|OCT}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|NOV}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|NOV}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|DEC}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|DEC}}

; Examples for all standard month numbers<nowiki>:</nowiki>
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|1}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|1}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|2}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|2}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|3}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|3}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|4}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|4}}
