: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|10}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|10}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|11}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|11}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|12}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|12}}

; Examples for month numbers with extra leading zero<nowiki>:</nowiki>
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|01}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|01}}
: <tt><nowiki>{{MONTHABBREV|02}}</nowiki></tt> returns {{MONTHABBREV|02}}
