== Table of Contents ==
#[[/Elements and Atoms: The Basics of Chemistry/]]{{status|0%}}

A more thorough table of contents, denoted by sections is listed lower in this page.

== Intention ==
This book is intended to serve as a college level text in a first semester Chemistry course. It is being created to accompany a Wikiversity course of the same title, soon to be developed.

