'''Introduction to this book'''

Words are power. They have power over people's minds. Behind every event which changed the course of history are words of great orators. 

This book will analyze the orators and their speeches and try to find out what makes them and their words great. 

<!-- Oratory is an art of effective communication with a group of people in order to influence, entertain or motivate them. -->

<div style="float:left;margin-left:10px;">{{Oratory and Rhetoric/Table of Contents}}</div>


