{{documentation subpage}}
=== Usage === This template may be used to add a Wikinews link to a page.
Links to pages on the Wikinews site: *{{tlx|Wikinews}}: Creates a box with link to a Wikinews page with the same name as the current page. *{{tlx|Wikinews|SomeArticleTitle}}: Creates a box with a link to the article ''SomeArticleTitle''. *{{tlx|Wikinews|SomeArticleTitle|LinkTitle}}: Creates a box with a link to the article ''SomeArticleTitle'' and with ''LinkTitle'' as the text displayed for the link. <includeonly> <!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE --> [[Category:Wikinews link templates| ]] </includeonly>

