</noinclude>

{{documentation subpage}}
=== Usage === This template may be used to add a link to a Wikinews category to a page.
*{{tlx|Wikinews category}}: Creates a box with a link to a Wikinews category with the same name as the current page. *{{tlx|Wikinews category|SomeCategoryTitle}}: Creates a box with a link to the category ''SomeCategoryTitle''. *{{tlx|Wikinews category|SomeCategoryTitle|LinkTitle}}: Creates a box with a link to the category ''SomeCategoryTitle'' and with ''LinkTitle'' as the text displayed for the link. <includeonly> <!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE --> [[Category:Wikinews link templates|Category]] </includeonly>

