<div style="margin-left: 10px;"> '''''{{sec link auto| wikinews | Portal:{{#if:x| {{{1}}} }} | {{{1}}} }}''''' </div>   <!-- {{#if:x|}} strips whitespace. -->
}}<noinclude>
{{documentation}}
</noinclude>

{{documentation subpage}}
=== Usage === This template may be used to add a Wikinews link to a page.
Links to pages on the Wikinews site: *{{tlx|Wikinews}}: Creates a box with link to a Wikinews portal with the same name as the current page. *{{tlx|Wikinews|SomeArticleTitle}}: Creates a box with a link to the portal ''SomePortalTitle''. Do not include the <tt>Portal:</tt> portion of the name. <includeonly> <!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE --> [[Category:Wikinews link templates|Portal]] </includeonly>

